PT-5。 奥尔特曼在今年早些时候透露：“GPT-5将整合语音交互、画布(Canvas)、深度搜索、深度研究等功能。”他提到的是OpenAI在过去几个月中在ChatGPT中推出的一系列功能。他还表示：“我们的一个重要目标是通过创建能够使用我们所有工具的系统，能够判断何时需要深入思考、何时不需要，并且能够广泛应用于各种任务，来统一我们的大模型。” 与此同时，OpenAI正面临来自竞争对手日益增长的压力，这些竞争对手采用了“开放”的方式来推出模型，例如中国的AI实验室DeepSeek。与OpenAI的策略不同，这些“开放”的竞争对手将他们的模型提供给人工智能社区用于实验，在某些情况下还用于商业化。 不过就在近日，奥尔特曼也宣布OpenAI将在未来几个月内发布一个“强大的带有推理能力的全新开放权重(open-weight)模型”。该模型将具有推理能力，并将接受额外的安全评估。 https://baijiahao.baidu.com/s?id=1828503111336906969&wfr=spider&for=pc"},"attached_info":"CkgI5fDv4pnRmSUQAxoJMTE0MzM3NjcxIIjvwb8GMAA4J0ATchMxODkxNzY3MzcxMDY2MjA4NTEyeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"81 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":""}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"20_1744288238.163318","card_id":"Q_1887462772205385513","card_label":{"type":"new","icon":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a4b0b52b561281109c51e4957cb20130_1440w.png","night_icon":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-10ef6526c602e55a8c606e46aa0cc586_1440w.png"},"target":{"id":1887462772205385500,"title":"知乎直答新推出的 「@ 快捷引用」功能，都有哪些有趣玩法？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/1887462772205385513","type":"question","created":1742786192,"answer_count":83,"follower_count":131,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[2,220,630,1707,3575023],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"知一声：直答「焕新升级」| 给你更专业、更可信的答案"},"attached_info":"CkkI5fDv4pnRmSUQAxoJMTE0MTQyNTg3IJCdg78GMAA4gwFAFHITMTg4NzQ2Mjc3MjIwNTM4NTUxM3gAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA","detail_text":"79 万热度","trend":0,"debut":true,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-055dfc3b2d361b49b6cb2a8c605acd70_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"21_1744288238.165644","card_id":"Q_1893453099936501910","target":{"id":1893453099936502000,"title":"如何评价《崩坏：星穹铁道》中的角色那刻夏？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/1893453099936501910